<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.7">
<l>pāru nīreri kāṟṟi ṉōṭuvā  kāca mumivai yāyiṉāṉ</l>
<l>pēru māyiram pēca niṉṟapi ṟappi liperu kumiṭam</l>
<l>kārum vārppaṉi nīḷvi cumpiṭaic cōru māmukil tōytara</l>
<l>cērum vārpoḻil cūḻe ḻiltiru vēṅka ṭamaṭai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, take refuge at beautiful Tiruvēṅkaṭam encircled by broad forests</l>
<l>As great clouds, where rain and dripping mist trickle in the high heavens, gather aimlessly,</l>
<l>The place where prospers the birthless one</l>
<l rend="indent">who remains [there] so [devotees] may speak [his] one-thousand names,</l>
<l>The one who became the atmosphere, as well as the earth, water, fire, and wind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
